How to run Kaybot locally (development):
1. (Optional but recommended) Create a virtualenv:
   python -m venv venv
   source venv/bin/activate  # Linux/Mac
   venv\Scripts\activate    # Windows PowerShell

2. Install requirements:
   pip install -r requirements.txt

3. Set your OpenRouter API key (optional for online mode):
   export OPENROUTER_API_KEY='your_key_here'   # Linux/Mac
   setx OPENROUTER_API_KEY "your_key_here"   # Windows (restart needed)

4. Launch the app:
   python app.py

5. Open http://localhost:7860 in your browser. For Hugging Face Spaces, push the repo to your Space and ensure the dependencies are in requirements.txt
